#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.concat.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.concat"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:1 of
msgid ""
"Concatenate dataframe objects along a particular axis with optional set "
"logic along the other axes."
msgstr "沿着特定轴连接 dataframe 对象，并可选择在其他轴上应用集合逻辑。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:4 of
msgid ""
"Can also add a layer of hierarchical indexing on the concatenation axis, "
"which may be useful if the labels are the same (or overlapping) on the "
"passed axis number."
msgstr ""
"还可以在连接轴上添加一层分层索引，如果传递的轴编号上的标签相同（或重叠）"
"，这可能会很有用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:8 of
msgid ""
"If a mapping is passed, the sorted keys will be used as the `keys` "
"argument, unless it is passed, in which case the values will be selected "
"(see below). Any None objects will be dropped silently unless they are "
"all None in which case a ValueError will be raised."
msgstr ""
"如果传递了映射，则将使用排序后的键作为 `keys` 参数，除非已传递该参数，在"
"这种情况下将选择值（见下文）。任何 None 对象将被静默丢弃，除非它们全部为 "
"None，此时将引发 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:13 of
msgid "The axis to concatenate along."
msgstr "要连接的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:15 of
msgid "How to handle indexes on other axis (or axes)."
msgstr "如何处理其他轴上的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:17 of
msgid ""
"If True, do not use the index values along the concatenation axis. The "
"resulting axis will be labeled 0, ..., n - 1. This is useful if you are "
"concatenating objects where the concatenation axis does not have "
"meaningful indexing information. Note the index values on the other axes "
"are still respected in the join."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则不使用连接轴上的索引值。结果轴将被标记为 0, ..., n - 1。"
"如果你连接的对象的连接轴没有有意义的索引信息，则这很有用。请注意，其他"
"轴上的索引值在连接中仍然会被保留。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:23 of
msgid ""
"If multiple levels passed, should contain tuples. Construct hierarchical "
"index using the passed keys as the outermost level."
msgstr "如果传递了多个级别，则应包含元组。使用传递的键作为最外层构造分层索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:26 of
msgid ""
"Specific levels (unique values) to use for constructing a MultiIndex. "
"Otherwise they will be inferred from the keys."
msgstr "用于构造 MultiIndex 的特定级别（唯一值）。否则将从键中推断出来。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:29 of
msgid "Names for the levels in the resulting hierarchical index."
msgstr "结果分层索引中各级别的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:31 of
msgid ""
"Check whether the new concatenated axis contains duplicates. This can be "
"very expensive relative to the actual data concatenation."
msgstr "检查新的连接轴是否包含重复项。相对于实际的数据连接，这可能非常耗时。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:34 of
msgid ""
"Sort non-concatenation axis if it is not already aligned when `join` is "
"'outer'. This has no effect when ``join='inner'``, which already "
"preserves the order of the non-concatenation axis."
msgstr ""
"如果 `join` 为 'outer' 且非连接轴尚未对齐，则对其进行排序。当 ``join='"
"inner'`` 时无效，因为此时已经保留了非连接轴的顺序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:39 of
msgid "If False, do not copy data unnecessarily."
msgstr "如果为 False，则不必要时不复制数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:42 of
msgid ""
"When concatenating all ``Series`` along the index (axis=0), a ``Series`` "
"is returned. When ``objs`` contains at least one ``DataFrame``, a "
"``DataFrame`` is returned. When concatenating along the columns (axis=1),"
" a ``DataFrame`` is returned."
msgstr ""
"当沿索引（axis=0）连接所有 ``Series`` 时，返回一个 ``Series``。当 ``objs`"
"` 包含至少一个 ``DataFrame`` 时，返回一个 ``DataFrame``。当沿列（axis=1）"
"连接时，返回一个 ``DataFrame``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:50 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.append`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:51 of
msgid "Concatenate Series."
msgstr "连接 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:53 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.append`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:54 of
msgid "Concatenate DataFrames."
msgstr "连接 DataFrames。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:56 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.join`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:57 of
msgid "Join DataFrames using indexes."
msgstr "使用索引连接 DataFrames。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:59 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.merge`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:60 of
msgid "Merge DataFrames by indexes or columns."
msgstr "通过索引或列合并 DataFrames。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:63 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:64 of
msgid "The keys, levels, and names arguments are all optional."
msgstr "keys、levels 和 names 参数都是可选的。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:66 of
msgid ""
"A walkthrough of how this method fits in with other tools for combining "
"pandas objects can be found `here <https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-"
"docs/stable/user_guide/merging.html>`__."
msgstr ""
"有关此方法如何与其他组合 pandas 对象的工具配合使用的详细说明，请参见 `"
"此处 <https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/merging."
"html>`__。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:71 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:72 of
msgid "Combine two ``Series``."
msgstr "合并两个 ``Series``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:84 of
msgid ""
"Clear the existing index and reset it in the result by setting the "
"``ignore_index`` option to ``True``."
msgstr ""
"通过将 ``ignore_index`` 选项设置为 ``True``，清除现有索引并在结果中重置它"
"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:94 of
msgid ""
"Add a hierarchical index at the outermost level of the data with the "
"``keys`` option."
msgstr "使用 ``keys`` 选项在数据的最外层添加一个分层索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:104 of
msgid "Label the index keys you create with the ``names`` option."
msgstr "使用 ``names`` 选项为创建的索引键添加标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:115 of
msgid "Combine two ``DataFrame`` objects with identical columns."
msgstr "合并两个具有相同列的 ``DataFrame`` 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:136 of
msgid ""
"Combine ``DataFrame`` objects with overlapping columns and return "
"everything. Columns outside the intersection will be filled with ``NaN`` "
"values."
msgstr ""
"合并具有重叠列的 ``DataFrame`` 对象并返回所有内容。交集之外的列将用 ``NaN"
"`` 值填充。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:153 of
msgid ""
"Combine ``DataFrame`` objects with overlapping columns and return only "
"those that are shared by passing ``inner`` to the ``join`` keyword "
"argument."
msgstr ""
"合并具有重叠列的 ``DataFrame`` 对象，并通过向 ``join`` 关键字参数传递 ``"
"inner`` 来仅返回共享的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:164 of
msgid ""
"Combine ``DataFrame`` objects horizontally along the x axis by passing in"
" ``axis=1``."
msgstr "通过传入 ``axis=1`` 沿 x 轴水平合并 ``DataFrame`` 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.concat.concat:174 of
msgid ""
"Prevent the result from including duplicate index values with the "
"``verify_integrity`` option."
msgstr "使用 ``verify_integrity`` 选项防止结果包含重复的索引值。"

